The insert absorbs wetness while the suede cloth layer absorbs the moisture from baby’s skin, leaving them feeling dry and comfy!   Because they come complete with a waterproof outer layer you do not need a separate diaper cover. All Eco Baby diapers can be machine-washed.

These ergonomic breast shields can be worn during breastfeeding; moreover, due to being comfortable they will help you breastfeed longer.

Wouldn't you love to be able to capture those tiny little hands and feet before they get too big, Photos and Videos can't capture the shape in Three Dimensional in the way a fun and easy Do-It-Yourself Casting Kit can.We offer kits for 3D casting (100% replica) of hands & feet, which captures the wrinkles , lines shape of nails etc. of newborns, older children & adults hands & feet . It enhances the beauty of your kids room or drawing room. A memory forever and a perfect gift for new born ,birthdays, wedding & anniversary , awards or blessings of parents.You don't have to spend lots on having a stranger prepare a 3D cast of your baby's feet or hands. The job isn't difficult, and it doesn't require special skills. This product allows you to DIY the whole process - making it much more intimate.Procedure to Make the Impression:All you need to complete the task is an empty reusable plastic container or similar tub - suitably sized for the hand or foot you are casting (because when you pour in the plaster, you want the moulding to stand firmly upright).The smaller the hand the smaller the container should be to conserve material.Gloves are not necessary as the dried ALFINA peels off very easily.All this is explained properly in the tip sheet so its very straight forwardThis Newborn Baby kit, contains the materials to do TWO complete 3D replica castingThere is enough casting material for the following ages in this kit:0 to 6 months: 2 impressions/casts7 to 12 months : 1 impression/castKey FeaturesNon-ToxicEasy to do,Quick and No messWipes off cleanly using ordinary baby wipes or a wet clothThe mould is biodegradable and environmentally friendly.SpecificationsBrand - My Impression StudioType - 3D Baby Hands And Feet Casting KitRecommended Age - NewbornMould - Biodegradable and environmentally friendlyWeight - 500 gmBox Dimension - L 19.05 x B 13.97 x H 8.89 inchesItems included in the pack1 bag of molding powder (ALFINA)1 bag of casting stone powder (White stone)1 Bottle of Metallic Gold paint colour 1 Paint Brush1 Sandpaper and 1 Step by Step Instruction manualThis kit is hand packed in reusable high quality plastic container/boxNote: Also includes trial pack so you can do a trial run to get used to the process. productBaseInfoV1.title: My Impression Studio Keepsake(Metallic Rust)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Create Beautiful Hand and Foot 3D life-sized Impressions in the comfort of your home. Now you will never forget just how little your precious child was. Wouldn't you love to be able to capture those tiny little hands and feet before they get too big? Photos and Videos can't capture the shape in Three Dimensional in the way a fun and easy Do-It-Yourself Casting Kit can. This 3D casting (100% replica) of hands & feet kit captures the wrinkles, lines shape of nails etc. of newborns/infant baby's hands & feet . Why choose this Kit? Because it has been tested by hundreds of mothers and fathers to capture every tiny crease and wrinkle of their precious baby's hands and feet - creating a priceless keepsake. Its fun, safe and simple to do! The number of casts depends on age of baby and size of container you use. Procedure to Make the Impression: All you need to complete the task is an empty reusable plastic container or similar tub - suitably sized for the hand or foot you are casting (because when you pour in the plaster, you want the molding to stand firmly upright). The smaller the hand the smaller the container should be to conserve material. Gloves are not necessary as the dried ALFINA peels off very easily. All this is explained properly in the tip sheet so its very straight forward This Newborn Baby kit, contains the materials to do TWO complete 3D replica casting There is enough casting material for the following ages in this kit: 0 to 6 months: 2 impressions/casts 7 to 12 months : 1 impression/cast. Items included in the pack: 1 bag of molding powder (ALFINA), 1 bag of casting stone powder (White stone), 1 Bottle of Metallic Rust paint color, 1 Paint Brush, 1 Sandpaper and 1 Step by Step Instruction manual & video tutorial link. This kit is hand packed in reusable high quality plastic container/box. Note: Also includes trial pack so you can do a trial run to get used to the process. One Trial bag of Molding and casting powder each.
